        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "For the Independent Journal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "saturday february sixteenth seventeen eighty eight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "MADISON",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "To the People of the State of New York:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "THE SECOND charge against the House of Representatives is, that it will be too small to possess a due knowledge of the interests of its constituents.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "As this objection evidently proceeds from a comparison of the proposed number of representatives with the great extent of the United States, the number of their inhabitants, and the diversity of their interests, without taking into view at the same time the circumstances which will distinguish the Congress from other legislative bodies, the best answer that can be given to it will be a brief explanation of these peculiarities.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "In determining the extent of information required in the exercise of a particular authority, recourse then must be had to the objects within the purview of that authority.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "What are to be the objects of federal legislation?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "Those which are of most importance, and which seem most to require local knowledge, are commerce, taxation, and the militia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "A proper regulation of commerce requires much information, as has been elsewhere remarked; but as far as this information relates to the laws and local situation of each individual State, a very few representatives would be very sufficient vehicles of it to the federal councils.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "Taxation will consist, in a great measure, of duties which will be involved in the regulation of commerce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "So far the preceding remark is applicable to this object.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "As far as it may consist of internal collections, a more diffusive knowledge of the circumstances of the State may be necessary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "But will not this also be possessed in sufficient degree by a very few intelligent men, diffusively elected within the State?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "Besides this source of information, the laws of the State, framed by representatives from every part of it, will be almost of themselves a sufficient guide.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "To be fully sensible of the facility which will be given to this branch of federal legislation by the assistance of the State codes, we need only suppose for a moment that this or any other State were divided into a number of parts, each having and exercising within itself a power of local legislation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "Is it not evident that a degree of local information and preparatory labor would be found in the several volumes of their proceedings, which would very much shorten the labors of the general legislature, and render a much smaller number of members sufficient for it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000012_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000012_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The federal councils will derive great advantage from another circumstance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "(The observations made on the subject of taxation apply with greater force to the case of the militia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "(With regard to the regulation of the militia, there are scarcely any circumstances in reference to which local knowledge can be said to be necessary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The general face of the country, whether mountainous or level, most fit for the operations of infantry or cavalry, is almost the only consideration of this nature that can occur.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The attentive reader will discern that the reasoning here used, to prove the sufficiency of a moderate number of representatives, does not in any respect contradict what was urged on another occasion with regard to the extensive information which the representatives ought to possess, and the time that might be necessary for acquiring it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "This information, so far as it may relate to local objects, is rendered necessary and difficult, not by a difference of laws and local circumstances within a single State, but of those among different States.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "Were the interests and affairs of each individual State perfectly simple and uniform, a knowledge of them in one part would involve a knowledge of them in every other, and the whole State might be competently represented by a single member taken from any part of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "On a comparison of the different States together, we find a great dissimilarity in their laws, and in many other circumstances connected with the objects of federal legislation, with all of which the federal representatives ought to have some acquaintance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "Whilst a few representatives, therefore, from each State, may bring with them a due knowledge of their own State, every representative will have much information to acquire concerning all the other States.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The changes of time, as was formerly remarked, on the comparative situation of the different States, will have an assimilating effect.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The effect of time on the internal affairs of the States, taken singly, will be just the contrary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "At present some of the States are little more than a society of husbandmen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000015_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000015_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The foresight of the convention has accordingly taken care that the progress of population may be accompanied with a proper increase of the representative branch of the government.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The experience of Great Britain, which presents to mankind so many political lessons, both of the monitory and exemplary kind, and which has been frequently consulted in the course of these inquiries, corroborates the result of the reflections which we have just made.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The number of inhabitants in the two kingdoms of England and Scotland cannot be stated at less than eight millions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "The representatives of these eight millions in the House of Commons amount to five hundred and fifty eight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000016_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000016_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "On the contrary, it is notorious, that they are more frequently the representatives and instruments of the executive magistrate, than the guardians and advocates of the popular rights.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-851_131029_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/851/131029/851_131029_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-851",
        "content": "They might therefore, with great propriety, be considered as something more than a mere deduction from the real representatives of the nation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
